  <title>Concept</title>
  <conbody>
    <p id="concept-definition"><term>Concepts</term><indexterm>DITA concept</indexterm> answer &quot;What is...&quot; questions. They provide background information  about a product, interface, or task. The concept is a <xref href="dita-specialization.xml">specialization</xref> of the <xref href="generic-topic.xml">generic topic</xref>.</p>
    <fig>
      <title>DITA Concept opened in Serna.</title>
      <image href="dita-concept-opened-in-serna.png" align="center" placement="break"/>
    </fig>
    <p>You can find more information about concept topics at: <xref href="http://docs.oasis-open.org/dita/v1.1/OS/archspec/dita_spec_22_info_concepts.html" format="html"/>.</p>
  </conbody>
